  "prompt": "Where can you buy Lego blocks all in the same color?",
  "response": "You can buy Lego blocks in the same color from several places:\n\n1. **LEGO Official Website**: The official LEGO website often has sections for bulk purchases or individual pieces. You can sort by color and buy specific bricks.\n\n2. **BrickLink**: This is a popular marketplace where you can buy LEGO parts from various sellers. You can search for bricks by color and find a range of options.\n\n3. **Brick Owl**: Similar to BrickLink, Brick Owl is another marketplace for LEGO pieces where you can filter by color and find specific items.\n\n4. **eBay**: You can find lots of LEGO bricks, including those sold in specific colors. Look for listings that indicate the color.\n\n5. **Local Toy Stores**: Some local toy stores or specialty shops may offer bulk LEGO in different colors. It's worth checking your nearby stores.\n\n6. **Craft Stores**: Stores like Michael\u2019s or Hobby Lobby may have LEGO bricks available for purchase by color, especially in their craft or building sections.\n\n7. **Amazon**: You can find sets or bulk purchases of LEGO bricks in specific colors on Amazon.\n\nWhen purchasing, be sure to check the seller\u2019s ratings and reviews to ensure a good experience.",
